```

**How new bookmark props would flow:**
1. Add to `ReaderProps` interface (above)
2. Add to `Reader` function destructuring (lines 31-50)
3. Pass through to both `ScrollReader` and `PaginatedReader` (lines 53-90)
4. Add to respective `*ReaderProps` interfaces (`ScrollReaderProps` line 99, `PaginatedReaderProps` line 24)
5. Use in each reader's component logic

**Example flow in client.tsx:**
From `/Users/blittle/dev/pressy3/packages/pressy/src/runtime/client.tsx` lines 632-666:
```typescript
<Reader
  title={chapter?.title || chapterSlug}
